  08 Sep 2007; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org>
  mp3blaster-3.2.3-r1.ebuild:
  Properly control oss/sdl according to USE flags.

  28 Aug 2007; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org>
  mp3blaster-3.2.3-r1.ebuild:
  Playback is screwed on ppc, so explicitly mark as -ppc.

  17 Aug 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> mp3blaster-3.2.3-r1.ebuild:
  Disable broken feature, nas.

  11 Aug 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> mp3blaster-3.2.3-r1.ebuild:
  newthreads and libpth support is broken, disable them.

*mp3blaster-3.2.3-r1 (11 Aug 2007)

  11 Aug 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  +mp3blaster-3.2.3-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed depends, USE flags, dodoc, installation, and more.

  30 Jul 2007; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> mp3blaster-3.2.3.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc64; bug #187111

  01 Mar 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> mp3blaster-3.2.0.ebuild,
  mp3blaster-3.2.3.ebuild:
  Install splay bin and man as splay_mp3blaster to prevent collisions with
  media-sound/splay

*mp3blaster-3.2.3 (11 Dec 2006)

